      "description": "Looking for an inexpensive car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option that could make a great daily runabout, first car, or project for someone handy. A straightforward, affordable way to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. Priced to reflect its condition and still offer good value.",
