      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with cosmetic wear and age-related flaws, but it still presents as a solid platform for someone who wants dependable transportation or a capable project. The powertrain pulls smoothly, the chassis feels planted, and it has clearly benefited from routine upkeep over time. Not perfect, and priced accordingly, but a great opportunity to get into a practical, mechanically honest car without spending big money. If you want an affordable vehicle with usable life left and good bones, this one is worth a look.",
